data.name: UpdateCase
data.value: update CKT_CASE set LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, DUP_CASE_INDICATOR = @dupCaseIndicator where NUMB = @numb

data.name: UpdateInterstateCase
